t retirement into old age read more gifting strategies a gifting strategy offers a person the opportunity to help others while reducing future tax liability lifetime gifts to noncharitable and non spouse beneficiaries like those allocated at death are subject to taxation under the estate tax code read more     charitable bequests a charitable bequest is a request in either your will or living trust which provides that all or a portion of your estate is to be given to a charitable organization bequests can be given as cash securities closely held stock real estate or even tangible personal property jewelry cars etc the beneficiary of your life insurance can even be an organization school or other charity read more family limited partnerships family limited partnerships flp can be very advantageous in asset protection and estate planning flps reduce the value of an estate while allowing the owner to maintain full control of investments and assets included in the partnership read more life insurance trusts life insurance gives a person peace of mind that his or her loved ones will receive financial help through its proceeds in the event of death read more for more information or to schedule your free consultation click here or call         webmail  privacy policy  contact us  featured articles  featured articles   featured articles   web site by ingroup inc  paradigm financial llc  walsh drive suite  parsippany nj  phone   fax   team members  paradigm financial advisors llc paradigm financial advisors a “feeonly” registered investment advisory firm learn more view menu k fiduciary advice contact us client login click a logo below to login secure client vault schwab advisor services td ameritrade professional team janet sexauer financial planning associate janet is a financial planning associate and works very closely with the lead advisors in preparing reviewing and coordinating the ongoing financial investment estate and tax details for many pfa clients she has earned