ls as well as our exclusive �wealth builder� investment program regardless of the program our focus is to protect our clients’ assets from severe market downturns grow our clients’ wealth with above average market returns generate a stable lifetime monthly income for our clients during their retirement the ideal portfolio although we recognize that a perfect portfolio is unrealistic our signature “wealth builder” portfolio incorporates the features most important to us our clients and we believe to many other responsible investors these features include traditionally conservative risk level as measured by standard deviation and traditional stock to bond ratios limited but still  equivalent exposure to the stock market  for higher potential returns takes advantage of dollar cost averaging can provide reasonably consistent monthly income is simple to understand and manage doesn’t require a lot of time and attentioneffort doesn’t depend on market timing ability to predict the future back testing results have consistently outperformed the sp tm index over mid to long terms low expenses and fees doesn’t require a lot of trading in and out of positions gives you complete control of your investments doesn’t have any penalties associated with accessing your money is less volatile than the market as a whole therefore it can be less stressful what you must believe in order to work successfully with us our clients must share the fundamental beliefs upon which our investment method is based these are we do not believe in fortune tellers ie we do not believe that anyone can predict the future therefore we will not put our life’s earnings and future prosperity in their hands to gamble with we believe that the us stock market will perform in the same manner that it has for the last  years in other words it will fluctuate up and down we believe that in the long run capitalism and thus the us economy will continue to grow due to an ever increasing population demand technological innovations the innate human desire to progress and improve its’ condition we understand that it is more important to avoid losses in our portfolio than it is to try and overcome them with exceptional gains if you accept and agree with the above then we believe you will be interested in what we have to offer who our clients are  we work with people that have money worth protecting want to achieve higher than average returns with less risk want to develop a consistent dependable income during retirement want to understand what they own in their portfolio and why are more concerned with results than image are realistic and pragmatic can recognize opportunity are tired of risking their assets in the wall street casino   b bill and leah have over  years of combined experience in the financial services industry managing our clients wealth and retirement savings is a huge privilege and responsibility we strive to provide the most competent and enlightened advice and personal service      questions you should consider     asset protection asset growth personal annuity             paradigm financial advisors is a georgia registered investment advisor crd  if you are not a resident of the state noted above all investmentrelated information on this site is for informational purposes only and does not constitute a solicitation or offer to sell securities over the internet  olivia lane ball ground ga  copyright   all rights reserved   paradigm financial advisors llc  perris ca  company information products resources my account talk to a db advisor  business directory ca perris investment advice investment advice paradigm financial advisors llc p paradigm financial advisors llc claim this business  n perris blvd ste g perris ca  get directions business info founded  incorporated ca annual revenue  employee count  industries investment advice contacts young choi contact business your email address subject message send message company summary paradigm financial advisors llc was found